Some possible future additions 

(if you'd like to try your chops at one of these, just fork the
project at GitHub.)


* Add a base lexicon using WordNet

* Add a simple example English grammar

* More examples so as to complete the complexity continuum

* A sqlite3 backed lexicon and ontology example

* Handle backtracking using exceptions

* Web-based visualization tool for the semantic annotations

* Complete the Tarot example


Pipe dreams

* Add the Penman Upper Model as an ontology [1]

* Add a statistical generation component that'll "fill-in-the-blanks" given weaker semantics.


[1] http://www.fb10.uni-bremen.de/anglistik/langpro/kpml/um89/um89-root.htm